item.title: About
item.description: About I am a sophomore at Thomas Jefferson High School for Science and Technology in Northern Virginia. Some things I like to do include crew, coding, playing chess, and more. This site is my portion of the internet. It contains projects, my resume, the occasional blog post, and more. This site was largely inspirited by Jonathan Buchholz1. This site was made using Markdown as the main language and Hugo as a framework for building the site.
